org.tensorics.core.expressions

Class BinaryOperationExpression<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorics.core.tree.domain.AbstractDeferredExpression<T>
      • org.tensorics.core.expressions.BinaryOperationExpression<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the results of the operands (and the result of the expression)
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Expression<T>, Node

    public class BinaryOperationExpression<T>
extends AbstractDeferredExpression<T>
    An unresolved expression which can be resolved by applying a binary operation on the results of the two operands (left, right). An instance contains the binary operation itself as well as expressions for both operands.
